Overview

Desktop attendance and access-control management software. It connects with Realtime biometric devices (fingerprint, face, RFID) to record employee attendance, manage shifts, generate reports, and control door access. Version 12.6 includes improved device compatibility, faster data syncing, and an updated user interface for easier HR and admin use.
